text: Marcel Leineweber (7 December 1912 - 5 November 1969) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1969 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pétange
